msgstr "<image id=\"img_id1621753\" src=\"media/helpimg/what-if.png\"><alt id=\"alt_id1621753\">περιοχή φύλλου what-if</alt></image>"

#. KavvR
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145239\n"
"help.text"
